In early 1902, Einstein and '
Reference: Mileva Marić ''
Text: ' (Милева Марић) had a daughter they named '
Reference: Lieserl Einstein 'Lieserl'
Text: ' in their correspondence, who was born in '
Reference: Novi Sad ''
Text: ' where Marić's parents lived.'
Open Tag: ref attributes: []
Text: 'This conclusion is from Einstein's correspondence with Marić. Lieserl is first mentioned in a letter from Einstein to Marić (who was staying with her family in or near Novi Sad at the time of Lieserl's birth) dated 4 February 1902 (''Collected papers'' Vol. 1, document 134).'
