Text: '

'
Reference: File:Albert Einstein at Princeton.jpg 'thumb|Einstein at his home in Princeton, 1949'
Text: '
After the death of Israel's first president, '
Reference: Chaim Weizmann ''
Text: ', in November 1952, Prime Minister '
Reference: David Ben-Gurion ''
Text: ' offered Einstein the position of '
Reference: President of Israel ''
Text: ', a mostly ceremonial post.'
